               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡ with the Psalms of the Virgin</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title>መዝሙረ ፡ ድንግል: 151 Psalms of David, fol. 2r-177r; 15 biblical canticles, fol. 178r-194v; Song of Songs, fol. 195r-204v; Praises of Mary, fol. 205r-219r; Gate of Light, fol. 219r-225r
                        
                     </title>
                     <note>Spiritual meanings for the Hebrew letters in Psalm 118, fol. 140r-152r; Columetric rubrication in Psalm 150, fol. 175v-176r, and the tenth biblical canticle, fol. 189r-190r
                        
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
